WEBVTT

1
00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:24.500
你真是爛透了， 湯姆
You're a jerk, Thom.

2
00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:27.000
聽著希莉亞， 我們必須順著我們的感覺走
Look Celia, we have to follow our passions;

3
00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:30.500
... 你熱愛機械工學， 而我只是想去太空中耍帥一下
...you have your robotics, and I just want to be awesome in space.

4
00:00:30.800 --> 00:00:34.000
你為什麼不肯承認你被我的機械手臂嚇壞了？
Why don't you just admit that you're freaked out by my robot hand?

5
00:00:34.500 --> 00:00:36.000
我沒有害怕， 只是...
I'm not freaked out by- it's...

6
00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:38.000
... 好好好！
...alright! Fine!

7
00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:41.000
我承認 我被嚇傻了！ 我還做惡夢被它追著跑...
I'm freaked out! I have nightmares that I'm being chased...

8
00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:42.000
... 被這些巨大的奪命機器爪子追殺...
...by these giant robotic claws of death...

9
00:00:42.200 --> 00:00:45.000
隨便你怎麼說。 湯姆， 我們之間玩完了
"Fourty years later" Whatever, Thom. We're done.

10
00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:53.500
機器人記憶同步鎖定完成！
Robot's memory synced and locked!

11
00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:03.000
這個挺詭異的
This is pretty freaky.

12
00:01:57.000 --> 00:01:59.000
你是不是該下去了吧？
Shouldn't you be down there?

13
00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:13.000
我昨天聽到你們這些傢伙的談話
I heard you guys talking last night.

14
00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:18.000
你知道的， 這不是我的錯
It's not my fault, you know.

15
00:03:11.000 --> 00:03:12.000
準備好了嗎？
Are you ready?

16
00:03:13.000 --> 00:03:15.000
你當然準備好了， 你是個搖滾明星嘛
Of course you're ready, you're a rockstar.

17
00:03:17.000 --> 00:03:18.000
情況如何， 貝里？
How's it looking, Barley?

18
00:03:19.000 --> 00:03:21.000
我們應該有10分鐘左右的時間...
We should have about ten minutes...

19
00:03:21.500 --> 00:03:23.000
好的， 棒極了
Well that's perfect.

20
00:03:23.500 --> 00:03:26.500
一分鐘後開始！ 全部的系統啟動！ 對， 你也是， 快點！
We're on in one! All systems go! Yeah you, go!

21
00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:32.000
快！ 動起來！ 快快快！
Go! Move your asses! Go go go!

22
00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:37.000
這個我喜歡！ 拜託， 快！
I love it! Come on, go!

23
00:03:43.000 --> 00:03:44.000
很好
That's nice.

24
00:03:44.500 --> 00:03:45.700
沒什麼好擔心的
Nothing to worry about.

25
00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:47.000
湯姆
Thom.

26
00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:53.000
她在那
There she is.

27
00:03:53.500 --> 00:03:54.500
就是現在
Now.

28
00:03:55.000 --> 00:03:56.000
你是愛她的
You love her.

29
00:03:57.000 --> 00:03:58.500
她就是你的熱情
She is your passion!

30
00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:01.000
溫柔點
Be tender to her.

31
00:04:01.500 --> 00:04:04.500
要誠懇！ 溫柔些
Be honest! Eh- be tender.

32
00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:08.000
讓她回憶起什麼是愛
Remind her what love is.

33
00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:55.000
... 好， 開演！
...and, action!

34
00:04:56.500 --> 00:04:58.000
記憶覆寫開始！
Memory overwrite in progress!

35
00:04:59.000 --> 00:05:01.000
你真是爛透了， 湯姆！
You're a jerk, Thom!

36
00:05:02.500 --> 00:05:05.000
噢， 抱歉， 不好意思
Ohp- Sorry! Sorry.

37
00:05:16.000 --> 00:05:17.000
聽著， 希莉亞
Look Celia.

38
00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:20.000
我們必須順著我們的感覺走
We have to follow our passions.

39
00:05:21.000 --> 00:05:23.000
你熱愛機械工學...
You have your robotics...

40
00:05:25.000 --> 00:05:28.000
... 而我只是想去太空中耍帥一下
...and I just want to be awesome in space.

41
00:05:39.000 --> 00:05:41.000
好的， 它們來了。 還有兩分鐘！
Okay, they're coming. Two minutes left!

42
00:05:43.000 --> 00:05:44.000
快點， 湯姆！
Speed it up, Thom!

43
00:05:45.000 --> 00:05:46.000
生動一點！
Vivacissimo!

44
00:05:47.000 --> 00:05:50.000
你為什麼不肯承認被我的機械手臂嚇壞了？
Why don't you just admit that you're freaked out by my robot hand?

45
00:05:56.000 --> 00:05:59.000
聽著， 希莉亞， 我那時還年輕...
Listen Celia, I was young...

46
00:05:59.500 --> 00:06:01.000
... 只是個小屁孩
...and a dick.

47
00:06:01.000 --> 00:06:03.000
但是這不是毀滅這個世界的理由
But that's no reason to destroy the world.

48
00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:06.000
他為啥要這麼說？
Why does he do this?

49
00:06:06.500 --> 00:06:08.500
我們已經試過這個情景了！
We already tried that one!

50
00:06:11.500 --> 00:06:12.500
中止！
Abort!

51
00:06:13.000 --> 00:06:14.000
停！
Cut!

52
00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:15.000
噢啊啊啊！
Whoaaa!

53
00:06:19.000 --> 00:06:20.000
噢啊啊啊！
Whoaaa!

54
00:06:21.000 --> 00:06:23.000
不...
Nooooo!

55
00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:25.000
你傷透了我的心
You broke my heart.

56
00:06:26.000 --> 00:06:27.000
我知道
I know.

57
00:06:27.000 --> 00:06:29.000
你把我拋棄在地球上
You forgot me on earth.

58
00:06:29.000 --> 00:06:30.000
我知道
I know.

59
00:06:30.500 --> 00:06:33.000
我應該把你碎屍萬段
I should just crush you.

60
00:06:36.000 --> 00:06:37.000
對...
I'm-

61
00:06:47.000 --> 00:06:48.000
對不起
I'm sorry.

62
00:06:50.000 --> 00:06:51.000
說的很自然
Good ad-lib.

63
00:06:59.000 --> 00:07:00.500
這不是我的錯！
Not my fault!

64
00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:03.000
這次
This time.

65
00:07:08.000 --> 00:07:09.500
上面安靜點！
Quiet on set!

66
00:07:10.000 --> 00:07:11.000
我們沒時間了！
We're out of time!

67
00:08:13.000 --> 00:08:14.000
快點！
Come on!

68
00:08:22.000 --> 00:08:24.000
啊...
RAAAAAAAAH!

69
00:08:24.000 --> 00:08:25.000
記憶覆寫， 90%
Memory overwrite, 90%.

70
00:08:26.000 --> 00:08:28.000
隊長！ 我們必須放棄了！
Captain! We have to abort!

71
00:08:38.000 --> 00:08:40.000
這個世界已經不一樣了， 希莉亞...
The world's changed, Celia...

72
00:08:54.000 --> 00:08:56.000
... 或許， 我們也可以改變
...maybe we can too.

73
00:08:58.000 --> 00:08:59.000
記憶覆寫完成！
Memory overwrite complete!

74
00:09:19.000 --> 00:09:20.000
你知道嗎
You know.

75
00:09:22.000 --> 00:09:24.000
我們可以從中學到一課
There's a lesson to be learned from this.

76
00:09:26.000 --> 00:09:27.000
也是有可能更糟的
Could'a gone worse.

